      "content": "wait, you're saying i should take vitamin K2 to help with the warfarin? i thought warfarin's job is to stop blood from clotting too much, so wouldn't adding vitamin K make it fight against the medicine? and youre sure the 2mg is fine without checking with my doctor first? i just want to be sure i'm doing the right thing.",
